A cyberpunk cityscape at night where streams of glowing data packets flow like luminous rivers between towering server buildings, one sleek chrome tower in the foreground labeled with circuit-pattern designs routes brilliant orange and blue light streams toward a distant brutalist data center shrouded in neon fog, the data streams split and merge through floating geometric proxy nodes that pulse with energy, rain-slicked streets below reflect the electric glow, holographic cloud formations swirl above the routing tower, the entire scene rendered in deep teals, electric oranges, and vivid magentas with sharp architectural details and atmospheric haze
